{
  "bio": [
    "Grigory Anikeev owns ABI Group, a Russian conglomerate with interests in food, retail and real estate.",
    "ABI Product, the largest division of ABI Group, is the largest Russian producer of sausage products and frozen food with revenue of about $1 billion.",
    "Anikeev has been deputy of The State Duma, the lower house of the Russian parliament, since 2007, and is a member of President Vladimir Putin's United Russia Party.",
    "In 2020, Anikeev declared the highest annual income among State Duma deputies - 2.7 billion rubles ($38 million)."
  ],
  "about": [
    "ABI Group is an acronym for Anikeev Business Invest."
  ]
